OL,3,CMet makes 100 arrests ahead of Notting
OL,4,CHill Carnival in bid to deter trouble
OL,6,FPolice have arrested 100 people in a
OL,7,Fbid to deter those they say "pose the
OL,8,Fgreatest risk" to the safety of
OL,9,FNotting Hill Carnival.
OL,11,FOfficers carried out "intelligence-led
OL,12,Finterventions" and 21 people were
OL,13,Frecalled to prison, and 11 firearms
OL,14,Fand more than 40 knives seized, the
OL,15,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,17,FThe Met said 266 people either have
OL,18,Fpolice bail or probation licence
OL,19,Fconditions not to attend the carnival
OL,20,Fthis weekend.
