OL,4,CHill Carnival in bid to deter trouble
OL,6,FCommander Charmain Brenyah, the
OL,7,Fforce's spokeswoman for the event,
OL,8,Fsaid around one million people are
OL,9,Fexpected to be on the streets of west
OL,10,FLondon.
OL,12,FMs Brenyah said: "Our policing plan
OL,13,Fmakes tackling serious violence a
OL,14,Fpriority, which is why we've carried
OL,15,Fout intelligence-led interventions
OL,16,Fagainst those groups and individuals
OL,17,Fwho we have reason to believe pose the
OL,18,Fgreatest risk to the safety of other
OL,19,Fcarnival-goers.
