OL,6,F"We hope that this police activity
OL,7,Fwill be a significant deterrent for
OL,8,Fthose who otherwise might have been
OL,9,Fplanning to come and engage in
OL,10,Fviolence and other criminality."
OL,12,FThe Met said live facial recognition
OL,13,F(LFR) technology ` which captures
OL,14,Fpeople's faces in real-time CCTV
OL,15,Fcameras ` will be used on the approach
OL,16,Fto and from the carnival as well as
OL,17,Foutside the boundaries of the event.
