OL,6,FThe Equality and Human Rights
OL,7,FCommission (EHRC) said earlier this
OL,8,Fweek the force's rules and safeguards
OL,9,Fover using the tool "fall short", and
OL,10,Fcould have a "chilling effect" on
OL,11,Findividuals' rights when used.
OL,13,FCommissioner Sir Mark Rowley sought to
OL,14,Freassure campaign groups that the
OL,15,Ftechnology will be used without bias
OL,16,Famid concerns it is discriminatory.
OL,18,FThe force believes the tool is
OL,19,F"reliable and effective", and helps
OL,20,Fkeep Londoners safe.
