OL,3,CMet makes 100 arrests ahead of Notting
OL,4,CHill Carnival in bid to deter trouble
OL,6,FAlongside the use of LFR technology,
OL,7,Fthe Met also plans to install
OL,8,Fscreening arches at some of the
OL,9,Fbusiest entry points to the carnival,
OL,10,Fwhere stop-and-search powers will be
OL,11,Fused in a bid to keep weapons out.
OL,13,FThe force said intelligence has been
OL,14,Fshared nationally to identify violent
OL,15,Fgangs planning to attend while banning
OL,16,Forders are being sought for those with
OL,17,Fa history of violence or sexual
OL,18,Foffences.
