OL,6,FCrowd safety is also a "concern", with
OL,7,Fattendees urged to listen to
OL,8,Fdirections from stewards or officers,
OL,9,Fthe Met said.
OL,11,FTwo people were murdered at the
OL,12,Fcarnival last year ` Cher Maximen, who
OL,13,Fwas killed in front of her three-year-
OL,14,Fold daughter, and chef Mussie Imnetu.
